      "content": "these are a good start. i want to make sure the tension between these groups feels real. to help with the casting and the \"vibe\" of each crew, can you go deeper into the racial profiles for these? like, give me more specific details on the typical members of the Trash Kings vs the Eastside Butchers or the Korean gang. what are their typical personalities and roles based on their backgrounds? i want to make sure i'm not being too soft on the writing—give me the raw, unfiltered versions of how these groups would actually look and act on the street.",
